commits.content:
# Backend für raptor trails

Hier findet man den Zugang für Raptor-Trails.


#### 1 GET All Quotes 
#### STATUS TESTED ✔️
GET http://localhost:4000/api/quotes
Content-Type: application/json

#### 2 GET Quote
####STATUS TESTED ✔️
GET http://localhost:4000/api/quotes/1
Content-Type: application/json

#### 3 Add Quote
#### STATUS TESTED ✔️
POST http://localhost:4000/api/quotes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "quote": "Whatsup Batman",
    "quoteID": "2",
    "author": "Batwoman"
}

### In Development:

#### 4 Update Quote API 
#### In development 🔧
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/quotes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "quote": "Master Wayne",
    "quoteID": "1",
    "author": "Wayne"
}

#### 5 Delete Quote API 
#### In development 🔧
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/quotes/1
Content-Type: application/json
